00:01:10,752 --> 00:01:12,431
=Those Days=

2
00:01:12,431 --> 00:01:14,800
(Adapted from iceread.com novel
"You Xi" by Qingyang Wanxi)

3
00:01:15,220 --> 00:01:17,900
=Episode 3=

4
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,479
This is Nanzhou Police Department,

5
00:01:22,479 --> 00:01:23,520
Nanhu Precinct.

6
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,800
Are you Yu Jingxiang's daughter?

7
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,240
Yes, that's me.

8
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,720
I told you.

9
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:31,679
I told you she was.

10
00:01:31,679 --> 00:01:33,600
I'm an officer of Nanhu Precinct.

11
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,279
Yu Jingxiang is in our station now.

12
00:01:36,199 --> 00:01:37,160
Let me ask you again,

13
00:01:37,559 --> 00:01:39,119
are you Yu Jingxiang's daughter?

14
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,479
Yes, I am.

15
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:43,000
See?

16
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,000
Honey,

17
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,039
didn't I transfer you the money?

18
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,119
I want to see you.

19
00:01:47,119 --> 00:01:47,839
Mom...

20
00:01:49,119 --> 00:01:49,919
I'm warning you,

21
00:01:50,199 --> 00:01:51,240
the station is currently

22
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:53,360
verifying all your
identification records.

23
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,440
If we find out you've
used a false identity

24
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,560
or impersonated someone else,

25
00:01:57,199 --> 00:01:59,319
you'll be charged with fraud.

26
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:02,000
We'll open a formal investigation
according to the law.

27
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,240
Do you understand?

28
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,039
I'll ask you one last time,

29
00:02:07,759 --> 00:02:09,440
are you Yu Jingxiang's daughter?

30
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:12,839
Honey,

31
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,679
say something!

32
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:16,679
Say something!

33
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:18,599
You scammed Yu Jingxiang
out of 3,000 yuan.

34
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:20,410
You're going to
pay it back right now.

35
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:27,080
You're my daughter! I know it!

36
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,119
Mom, this is their stuff!

37
00:02:29,119 --> 00:02:29,920
This is their stuff!

38
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:30,879
It's their phone!

39
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:32,760
I'm sorry!

40
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:33,999
Let's go to the supermarket, Mom!

41
00:02:33,999 --> 00:02:35,250
There's a discount for the eggs.

42
00:02:35,399 --> 00:02:36,320
Let's go buy some eggs.

43
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:36,920
Come on.

44
00:02:37,119 --> 00:02:38,119
Easy there.

45
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:50,960
Hi, Mr. Feng.

46
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,320
Hi, Mingzhu.

47
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,279
Have a seat.

48
00:02:53,279 --> 00:02:53,839
Okay.

49
00:02:54,399 --> 00:02:55,119
Come, sit.

50
00:02:56,839 --> 00:02:57,719
Have some tea.

51
00:02:58,399 --> 00:02:59,520
It's fine, sir.

52
00:03:00,999 --> 00:03:02,320
I heard from Director Zhao

53
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,520
that you've moved all
your reception business

54
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,360
to our Nanxi Hotel.

55
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,760
I really appreciate that.

56
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,879
I wasn't sure what to bring,

57
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:10,080
so I got you some tea.

58
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,520
Jianqi said you're a tea lover.

59
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,420
Come on, we're family.

60
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:15,279
You shouldn't have.

61
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:16,760
Don't do this again next time.

62
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,200
I'm sorry for the other day.

63
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,320
My brother was a little harsh.

64
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:24,320
He made things awkward
for you and Mrs. Feng.

65
00:03:26,399 --> 00:03:28,520
We should've been more
considerate that day.

66
00:03:29,570 --> 00:03:31,420
A happy occasion got derailed
by heated words.

67
00:03:31,999 --> 00:03:33,480
Please talk to your parents

68
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,480
and calm them down.

69
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,360
I'll speak with Jianqi's mom too.

70
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:39,679
Her temper isn't great.

71
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,910
I hope for your understanding.

72
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,640
Anyway, this wedding

73
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:46,200
has to be both respectable and grand.

74
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:48,760
Honestly, I don't mind what
kind of wedding we have.

75
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:51,480
As my mom always says,
"A moment of glory

76
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,370
isn't as important as
a lifetime of stability."

77
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:54,960
Your mom is right.

78
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,360
But then again,

79
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,399
Mingzhu,

80
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,080
I've been in business

81
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,240
for years.

82
00:04:02,679 --> 00:04:04,200
I have friends,

83
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,480
leaders,

84
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,520
contacts from all walks
of life to consider.

85
00:04:08,119 --> 00:04:10,260
We have to put on a event
that reflects well on us.

86
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:12,439
Don't worry, leave everything to me.

87
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:14,480
Lijun Hotel is massive.

88
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,879
It can host over a hundred tables.

89
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:18,240
You must invite
all your relatives and friends.

90
00:04:19,119 --> 00:04:20,640
That puts me at ease.

91
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,640
I'll let Jianqi know right away.

92
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,650
Here, have some water.

93
00:04:24,679 --> 00:04:25,240
Here.

94
00:04:26,479 --> 00:04:27,399
How is Jianqi?

95
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,640
He's doing great.

96
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,320
He's even gained weight.

97
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,200
Focus on your work.

98
00:04:37,290 --> 00:04:39,000
Well, someone's feeling
generous after that feast.

99
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,530
Now you're out here
doing good deeds.

100
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,479
Oh, hardly.

101
00:04:41,599 --> 00:04:43,520
That whole bottle of water is his.

102
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,440
Drink more then.

103
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:45,960
Drink more.

104
00:04:46,650 --> 00:04:47,799
That meal was just too rich.

105
00:05:05,479 --> 00:05:06,039
Hello.

106
00:05:06,799 --> 00:05:07,479
Honey,

107
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,159
want to go swimming tonight?

108
00:05:10,719 --> 00:05:12,399
What's with the sudden urge to swim?

109
00:05:15,239 --> 00:05:17,479
I feel like I'm soaking
in brine right now.

110
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,719
I need a dip to dilute it a bit.

111
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,120
Still salty?

112
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:35,039
Not at all. It's sweet now.

113
00:05:35,599 --> 00:05:36,599
Want a taste?

114
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,399
Tell you what, let's have a race.

115
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,450
I'll give you a three-length head start.

116
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,880
You think you can outswim me?

117
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,560
Let's try it.

118
00:05:52,599 --> 00:05:53,399
I'll start then.

119
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:57,000
That's two body lengths.

120
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,399
That's three!

121
00:06:00,039 --> 00:06:00,880
I'm coming!

122
00:06:21,170 --> 00:06:22,359
What's the point of all this?

123
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,599
This is the price for
abandoning a child

124
00:06:25,599 --> 00:06:26,239
Dad.

125
00:06:27,599 --> 00:06:29,279
Mom is already heartbroken.

126
00:06:30,039 --> 00:06:31,239
That's enough.

127
00:06:43,239 --> 00:06:44,560
Try not to take it so hard.

128
00:06:45,479 --> 00:06:47,960
My little sister was given
away almost 30 years ago.

129
00:06:48,919 --> 00:06:50,520
She can't be found so quickly.

130
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,520
It's just going to

131
00:06:52,039 --> 00:06:54,039
take some time. Isn't it?

132
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:57,200
I lie awake night after night.

133
00:06:59,359 --> 00:07:01,039
The moment I close my eyes,

134
00:07:01,479 --> 00:07:05,640
I can hear the baby

135
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:08,680
crying and crying.

136
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:13,719
Your dad is right.

137
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,560
This is my punishment.

138
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,599
My karma.

139
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,200
Mom.

140
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:24,039
But you weren't the one
who gave her away.

141
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,359
- It was Grandma.
- No, it wasn't her fault.

142
00:07:26,359 --> 00:07:28,440
It wasn't your grandmother's fault.

143
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:32,120
When I was pregnant with your sister,

144
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:37,039
my work unit was going through layoffs.

145
00:07:37,479 --> 00:07:40,039
You know how I am.

146
00:07:40,479 --> 00:07:42,479
I was so proud.

147
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:46,760
I was terrified that having a child
would affect my work,

148
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,599
that they would let me go.

149
00:07:50,919 --> 00:07:51,799
Then...

150
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,000
When I found out

151
00:07:55,599 --> 00:07:57,560
I was having twins,

152
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,440
I thought,

153
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:02,039
"It's impossible. How will we manage?"

154
00:08:03,159 --> 00:08:04,159
I was so worried.

155
00:08:05,039 --> 00:08:06,799
I told your grandmother,

156
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,919
"We can't raise them both.

157
00:08:09,919 --> 00:08:12,880
How could we possibly manage?

158
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:17,200
If a good family wanted a child,

159
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,799
we could give one away."

160
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:21,919
I think your grandmother

161
00:08:24,159 --> 00:08:25,799
took me seriously.

162
00:08:29,159 --> 00:08:30,160
And back then, your dad...

163
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:31,520
Your dad was getting into trouble.

164
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:32,560
He got into a fight,

165
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:33,799
the police arrested him,

166
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,440
and he was sent to prison for years.

167
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,200
Mom...

168
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,919
Mom, please don't be like this.

169
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,560
Don't overthink it.

170
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,519
Now...

171
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,630
Right now, what matters most is

172
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,580
that we give it our all
to find my sister, okay?

173
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,719
Yes.

174
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:50,560
Yes.

175
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:52,599
We have to find your sister.

176
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,239
We have to...

177
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,400
But even if we do,

178
00:08:58,999 --> 00:09:02,200
then what?

179
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:05,160
What if she doesn't want to see me?

180
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:08,759
She probably hates me.

181
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:10,359
I should die.

182
00:09:10,359 --> 00:09:11,599
Oh, my gosh! Mom!

183
00:09:11,599 --> 00:09:12,440
Mom...

184
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,239
I should die.

185
00:09:13,239 --> 00:09:14,639
You're scaring me, Mom!

186
00:09:14,839 --> 00:09:15,719
I should die.

187
00:09:15,719 --> 00:09:18,200
Mom, I'm still pregnant.

188
00:09:23,119 --> 00:09:23,999
Oh, yes.

189
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:24,800
You're right.

190
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,119
It's okay, honey.

191
00:09:26,119 --> 00:09:28,440
I'm okay now.

192
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,800
I'm okay.

193
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,160
You should go home.

194
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:32,320
Jiao...

195
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,359
Jiao is waiting for you to come home.

196
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,359
I'm okay now.

197
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,080
I'm okay.

198
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,440
Go home.

199
00:09:39,479 --> 00:09:41,759
I'm okay.

200
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,759
Please enjoy your food.

201
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,440
(Alipay payment received, 3,000 yuan.)

202
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,359
Got your salary?

203
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,710
I transferred it to you immediately,
didn't even touch it.

204
00:09:56,479 --> 00:09:57,960
Is your 1,000 yuan monthly allowance

205
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,999
enough?

206
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,719
Since you're being so good,

207
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:01,960
I'll give you a raise.

208
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,639
No need.

209
00:10:03,359 --> 00:10:04,400
I just top up my phone,

210
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,359
I don't use credit,

211
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:07,460
I eat lunch in the cafeteria,
dinner with my parents.

212
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:08,879
I can buy you a few milk teas,

213
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:10,359
get you flowers on holidays.

214
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:12,999
Rhyming, huh?

215
00:10:16,719 --> 00:10:17,519
You're so annoying.

216
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:21,119
Hello.

217
00:10:21,119 --> 00:10:22,639
Where are you, Xu Zhidong?

218
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,599
Mom's been scammed.

219
00:10:23,599 --> 00:10:25,320
She's in really bad shape. Come home now.

220
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,519
Okay, I got it.

221
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,200
What's wrong?

222
00:10:34,999 --> 00:10:35,719
Nothing.

223
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,639
My sister says Mom's
not doing well emotionally.

224
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:38,879
Go home now.

225
00:10:38,970 --> 00:10:40,879
Don't worry about this,
I'll pack everything up.

226
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:41,440
Go!

227
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,160
Are you sure?

228
00:10:43,430 --> 00:10:44,560
I bought the groupon coupon.

229
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,759
I'll send it to you later.

230
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,960
Zhidong.

231
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,639
Yes?

232
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,400
Don't ride too fast.

233
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,040
Zhixia.

234
00:11:03,359 --> 00:11:04,800
What took you so long?

235
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,239
I was eating with Bichen.

236
00:11:06,239 --> 00:11:07,080
I left as soon

237
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,960
as I got your call.

238
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:08,879
I didn't wait.

239
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,879
You could've just told me
on the phone.

240
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,040
I wouldn't dare.

241
00:11:12,350 --> 00:11:14,320
If Bichen dumps me,
you have take responsibility.

242
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,070
Right, I have to take responsibility
for everything.

243
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,599
I'm your sister, not your mother.

244
00:11:17,599 --> 00:11:19,040
You're just a mother to me.

245
00:11:20,359 --> 00:11:21,920
How's Mom doing?

246
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,239
Same as before.

247
00:11:23,239 --> 00:11:25,450
Sighing nonstop, looking
like she's lost the will to live.

248
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,960
Listen,

249
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:28,800
you'd better keep an eye on her.

250
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,879
She gave you all her pension money.

251
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:31,920
If she does something stupid,

252
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:32,639
we'll both be motherless,

253
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:33,950
and you'll be broke on top of that.

254
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,719
I've got to go. Jiao's waiting
for me to have dinner.

255
00:11:35,719 --> 00:11:36,759
Take care on your way back.

256
00:11:37,359 --> 00:11:38,280
Keep an eye on her.

257
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,040
You hear me?

258
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:39,639
Got it.

259
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,160
Thanks.

260
00:11:49,239 --> 00:11:49,999
Sweetheart,

261
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,920
I've never asked you this.

262
00:11:57,759 --> 00:11:59,359
Do you resent your birth parents?

263
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:04,479
No, I don't.

264
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:09,999
If they hadn't given me away,

265
00:12:10,410 --> 00:12:12,080
I wouldn't have
a wonderful mom like you.

266
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:19,320
You should...

267
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:20,800
Leave this to me.

268
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:24,239
Jianqi and Minghui are painting.

269
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:26,479
Take the strawberries you
just washed over to them.

270
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,960
Hey, Minghui,

271
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,800
did you add salt in my lunch?

272
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:38,599
Feng Jianqi,

273
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:40,999
don't you dare make
baseless accusations.

274
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:43,760
If you keep slandering me like this,
I'll sue you for defamation.

275
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:47,920
Minghui.

276
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:48,920
What?

277
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:51,200
Don't mistake my kindness for weakness.

278
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:53,040
Let me tell you, people your size

279
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,599
are easy to take down.

280
00:12:56,599 --> 00:12:57,440
Feng Jianqi,

281
00:12:58,460 --> 00:13:00,400
you're the one who's
been crashing at our place

282
00:13:00,599 --> 00:13:01,879
and hogging my room.

283
