00:25:37,840 --> 00:25:38,999
they're getting worse.

567
00:25:39,079 --> 00:25:39,759
Why?

568
00:25:41,360 --> 00:25:43,880
He just hasn't been in the right
headspace for studying lately.

569
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:44,960
That's putting it mildly.

570
00:25:45,450 --> 00:25:46,960
He's not "out of the right headspace,"

571
00:25:47,479 --> 00:25:49,079
he has no headspace for it at all.

572
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,079
Of course,

573
00:25:52,519 --> 00:25:54,680
he's very active in other areas.

574
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,479
What other areas?

575
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,759
He brought a snake to school

576
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:02,400
and nearly scared Lu Bing to death.

577
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,759
Do you know who Lu Bing is?

578
00:26:03,759 --> 00:26:05,759
She's our top student

579
00:26:05,799 --> 00:26:07,960
She got into a top-tier
university last year

580
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,759
but didn't go.

581
00:26:08,760 --> 00:26:09,880
She's repeating her final year

582
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:12,050
specifically to aim for
Tsinghua or Peking University.

583
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:14,960
Wow, that's quite the gap between them.

584
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,759
But don't worry, Mr. Sun,

585
00:26:17,999 --> 00:26:19,960
the situation with Lu Bing
has been resolved.

586
00:26:20,799 --> 00:26:21,600
Resolved? How?

587
00:26:22,079 --> 00:26:24,279
Lu Bing's brother came
over with some guys

588
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:26,600
and beat up Minghui's brother-in-law.

589
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:28,239
Even though they got the wrong guy,

590
00:26:28,239 --> 00:26:29,920
their family got it out of their system.

591
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:34,560
Good that it's resolved.

592
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,680
Anyway, here's the thing,

593
00:26:36,999 --> 00:26:39,360
we need to fix Minghui's

594
00:26:39,479 --> 00:26:41,160
academic problem immediately.

595
00:26:42,279 --> 00:26:44,279
He's a bright kid.

596
00:26:44,279 --> 00:26:45,239
Yes, he is.

597
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:47,220
But he can't stay stuck
in his senior year forever.

598
00:26:47,239 --> 00:26:48,160
You're right.

599
00:26:48,519 --> 00:26:49,360
Let's work together,

600
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:51,719
the school and your family,

601
00:26:51,999 --> 00:26:53,840
to help him make some real progress.

602
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:55,160
Let's push hard this year

603
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,360
and get his grades up.

604
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,440
Got it. We'll push him.

605
00:27:07,239 --> 00:27:08,200
Mom and Dad.

606
00:27:08,799 --> 00:27:09,719
I'm home.

607
00:27:10,559 --> 00:27:11,400
You're home.

608
00:27:12,559 --> 00:27:13,319
How did it go?

609
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,960
What did the school say?

610
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:17,200
Let me have some water first.

611
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:20,880
Easy there.

612
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:21,640
How did it go?

613
00:27:23,479 --> 00:27:24,600
His teacher said a lot,

614
00:27:24,799 --> 00:27:25,880
but to sum it up,

615
00:27:26,410 --> 00:27:29,160
Nanzhou High School just wants to
get Minghui out as soon as possible.

616
00:27:29,759 --> 00:27:30,759
Out? To where?

617
00:27:30,759 --> 00:27:32,200
To college, of course.

618
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:34,360
They've had enough of him.

619
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,279
Oh, stop joking.

620
00:27:35,279 --> 00:27:36,120
College?

621
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:37,680
You think you can
just send him there?

622
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:39,120
Your family owns
the university now?

623
00:27:39,130 --> 00:27:40,120
You have to pass the exams to get in!

624
00:27:40,120 --> 00:27:41,920
You think I'm talking
about direct admission?

625
00:27:41,930 --> 00:27:43,350
The teachers are desperate.

626
00:27:43,350 --> 00:27:45,279
They said as long as
Minghui's willing to study,

627
00:27:45,279 --> 00:27:46,719
they'll even give him extra tutoring.

628
00:27:47,520 --> 00:27:49,479
No, no, we can't trouble
the teachers like that.

629
00:27:49,479 --> 00:27:51,079
They're busy
with all the graduating students.

630
00:27:51,079 --> 00:27:51,799
Yes.

631
00:27:51,799 --> 00:27:53,940
It's not right for them to
tutor our kid on top of that.

632
00:27:53,950 --> 00:27:56,880
We can't just dump
everything on the school.

633
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,479
That's not right.

634
00:27:58,559 --> 00:27:59,999
Then who do we dump

635
00:27:59,999 --> 00:28:00,799
it on?

636
00:28:04,759 --> 00:28:05,759
It's our family's issue.

637
00:28:05,759 --> 00:28:07,200
We should handle it ourselves,

638
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:07,759
right?

639
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:10,559
What does that mean? Dump him on Jianqi?

640
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,279
Good idea.

641
00:28:15,840 --> 00:28:17,640
You want me to tutor Minghui?

642
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:19,920
His English is the worst.

643
00:28:20,039 --> 00:28:21,400
Start with that.

644
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:23,799
Honey,

645
00:28:24,319 --> 00:28:24,880
do you realize

646
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:26,799
your brother's been bullying me?

647
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:27,759
I know.

648
00:28:28,039 --> 00:28:29,479
Just be the bigger person.

649
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:31,799
My mom bullies my dad all the time too.

650
00:28:32,319 --> 00:28:33,360
That's different.

651
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,120
Honey,

652
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:36,880
does your mom put
salt in your dad's lunch?

653
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:39,160
Does she turn off the hot water
while he's showering?

654
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:41,120
Does she turn off

655
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:41,759
the water

656
00:28:41,759 --> 00:28:43,360
and throw a snake in there?

657
00:28:43,479 --> 00:28:45,160
A snake! A live snake!

658
00:28:46,039 --> 00:28:46,920
Honey,

659
00:28:47,120 --> 00:28:48,719
your English is so amazing!

660
00:28:48,719 --> 00:28:49,550
You just switch to it

661
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:51,430
like it's your native language
when it matters.

662
00:28:52,319 --> 00:28:53,640
Please teach Minghui.

663
00:28:53,999 --> 00:28:54,680
Honey,

664
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:57,279
hearing you praise me like that

665
00:28:57,279 --> 00:28:58,799
makes me feel blessed,

666
00:28:58,799 --> 00:28:59,999
but tutoring Minghui?

667
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:01,400
Sorry, that's a no.

668
00:29:03,479 --> 00:29:05,680
Look, just put up with my brother

669
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,559
for now.

670
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,440
When your sister ever bullies me,

671
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,350
I'll put up with it too.

672
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:12,160
Your sister's not exactly
easy to deal with either.

673
00:29:14,279 --> 00:29:15,079
Okay?

674
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,400
Fine, fine.

675
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:24,200
But at least make him
get rid of that snake first.

676
00:29:26,559 --> 00:29:27,319
Little Hui.

677
00:29:28,479 --> 00:29:29,120
Go on.

678
00:29:29,759 --> 00:29:30,999
It's not that I don't want you,

679
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,940
it's that Grandma and Grandpa
don't want you anymore.

680
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:35,680
Go on, get out of here.

681
00:29:38,799 --> 00:29:40,640
I let it go. Happy now?

682
00:29:44,719 --> 00:29:45,759
He looks reluctant.

683
00:29:46,039 --> 00:29:47,120
He didn't want to let it go.

684
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,239
Stay back, it might bite you.

685
00:29:50,239 --> 00:29:51,400
It's not going to bite.

686
00:29:51,519 --> 00:29:52,759
Snakes bite.

687
00:29:59,799 --> 00:30:00,559
Come in.

688
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:09,840
Alright, what are we studying?

689
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:11,950
Where's your English textbook?

690
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:13,239
English...

691
00:30:16,039 --> 00:30:18,160
English book.

692
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:24,440
Let's see what you've got.

693
00:30:27,759 --> 00:30:29,719
This book is falling apart.

694
00:30:29,719 --> 00:30:31,370
This is what "well-worn
from reading" looks like.

695
00:30:31,799 --> 00:30:32,840
Didn't you know?

696
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:34,750
Sure, let's wear this
one out a little more.

697
00:30:35,039 --> 00:30:36,680
Sit up straight, feet down.

698
00:30:40,719 --> 00:30:41,799
Open to Unit One.

699
00:30:42,239 --> 00:30:43,719
Read it aloud, let me hear you.

700
00:30:47,719 --> 00:30:48,360
Open your mouth.

701
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:53,160
"The Art History."

702
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,239
Minghui reads really well.

703
00:30:55,079 --> 00:30:57,400
His English sounds great.

704
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:59,200
See, he does like to learn.

705
00:30:59,519 --> 00:31:01,079
He just never had the right teacher.

706
00:31:01,079 --> 00:31:03,920
"It's hard to give a..."

707
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:05,719
What's so funny?

708
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:07,400
Nothing.

709
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,920
"Precise definition."

710
00:31:10,759 --> 00:31:12,719
Jianqi's English was
great back in college.

711
00:31:12,799 --> 00:31:13,479
Mingzhu.

712
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:17,479
I felt so relieved when I heard Jianqi

713
00:31:17,479 --> 00:31:18,880
was tutoring your brother.

714
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,450
And the best part is, it's free.

715
00:31:20,559 --> 00:31:22,799
Yes, makes the wallet feel even better.

716
00:31:24,719 --> 00:31:27,200
Is about a foot of space
enough for you two here?

717
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,039
Yes.

718
00:31:28,239 --> 00:31:29,120
I think it's enough.

719
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,120
It's enough.

720
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:31,880
"Watching..."

721
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:33,239
Stop.

722
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:35,239
Listen up.

723
00:31:35,559 --> 00:31:38,360
When an infinitive is the subject,
the verb must be singular.

724
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:39,319
For example,

725
00:31:39,799 --> 00:31:41,319
"Watching TV is boring."

726
00:31:44,799 --> 00:31:45,479
Jianqi,

727
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:50,120
I didn't actually set
the little snake free.

728
00:31:51,759 --> 00:31:52,960
I hid it.

729
00:31:55,650 --> 00:31:56,600
Where did you hide it?

730
00:31:57,719 --> 00:31:58,920
Where did I hide it?

731
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:02,039
I hid it...

732
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:03,600
I hid it...

733
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:06,079
Here!

734
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:09,360
Minghui!

735
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:10,279
No!

736
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:15,799
- Shen Minghui!
- Jianqi!

737
00:32:18,039 --> 00:32:18,719
Jianqi!

738
00:32:18,719 --> 00:32:19,279
Minghui!

739
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:19,840
Jianqi!

740
00:32:20,479 --> 00:32:21,759
- You little brat!
- I got you!

741
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:23,279
You're asking for a spanking!

742
00:32:23,519 --> 00:32:23,960
Pull me up!

743
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,239
I'm going to teach you a lesson!

744
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:26,759
You're stuck.

745
00:32:26,759 --> 00:32:27,400
Jianqi,

746
00:32:27,559 --> 00:32:28,690
I can't even save myself now.

747
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:29,999
You're on your own, I can't help you!

748
00:32:29,999 --> 00:32:30,519
Minghui!

749
00:32:30,799 --> 00:32:31,440
Minghui!

750
00:32:32,239 --> 00:32:32,559
Jianqi!

751
00:32:32,559 --> 00:32:33,920
You're asking for it!

752
00:32:34,559 --> 00:32:35,400
Stop right there!

753
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:36,960
Climb, Jianqi!

754
00:32:37,039 --> 00:32:38,120
Mom!

755
00:32:38,559 --> 00:32:40,039
Stop right there, Shen Jianqi!

756
00:32:40,039 --> 00:32:40,719
I'm sorry!

757
00:32:40,719 --> 00:32:41,120
Watch it!

758
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:43,120
Mom, stop chasing me!

759
00:32:43,479 --> 00:32:44,400
You little brat!

760
00:32:44,840 --> 00:32:45,360
Mom!

761
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:47,079
Why did you have to be so mischievous?

762
00:32:47,410 --> 00:32:48,840
My princess! I'm sorry! Please stop!

763
00:32:48,840 --> 00:32:50,600
Princess, my foot!

764
00:32:51,279 --> 00:32:52,319
Mom, don't come any closer!

765
00:32:52,759 --> 00:32:53,999
Stop chasing me, Mom!

766
00:32:54,279 --> 00:32:54,960
Mom!

767
00:32:55,519 --> 00:32:56,079
Mom!

768
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:57,400
You're becoming like a three-year-old!

769
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,840
Come any closer, and I'll jump!

770
00:32:58,840 --> 00:33:00,600
Go ahead! Jump!

771
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:01,950
It's not like you're fast
enough to catch me.

772
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:02,840
I'm not fast enough?

773
00:33:02,840 --> 00:33:03,799
I'm going to kill you!

774
00:33:03,799 --> 00:33:04,600
I have to run!

775
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:05,270
Stop right there!

776
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:05,960
I have to go!

777
00:33:06,079 --> 00:33:07,039
Stop right there!

778
00:33:07,039 --> 00:33:07,920
Run faster if you can!

779
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:08,999
You little rascal,

780
00:33:09,999 --> 00:33:11,799
are you trying to drive me mad?

781
00:33:13,799 --> 00:33:16,360
Their family is probably
lively and happy right now.

782
00:33:16,519 --> 00:33:18,880
Meanwhile, our place is so
quiet that even the TV echoes.

783
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:24,239
Maybe

784
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,920
we should pick a day

785
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:30,239
for both families to sit down
and talk again.

786
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,120
No.

787
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:33,039
There's nothing to talk about.

788
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,279
It's a power game now.

789
00:33:36,120 --> 00:33:37,120
If we back down,

790
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:40,319
they'll walk all over us.

791
00:33:40,319 --> 00:33:42,039
But we're a family now.

792
00:33:43,319 --> 00:33:44,120
I just think

793
00:33:45,759 --> 00:33:47,360
we should try to handle things

794
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:48,559
with a little goodwill.

795
00:33:49,400 --> 00:33:51,440
What do you mean, "a family"?
Since when?

796
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,120
It's ridiculous.

797
00:33:52,650 --> 00:33:54,239
Our families aren't even well-matched.

798
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,560
You think getting a marriage
certificate makes us family?

799
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:57,759
It's not that simple.

800
00:33:59,759 --> 00:34:01,279
Why are you being so stubborn?

801
00:34:01,279 --> 00:34:03,400
Stubborn? Who's being stubborn?

802
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:04,759
I'm being stubborn?

803
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:07,719
I'm just

804
00:34:08,680 --> 00:34:10,759
setting the ground rules straight.

805
00:34:11,759 --> 00:34:14,559
They shouldn't think it's so easy
to marry into our family.

806
00:34:20,999 --> 00:34:21,800
Hello, Mr. Yu.

807
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:22,840
Could you wait?

808
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:24,119
I'll coming right away.

809
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:27,119
Who is it? You're going out?

810
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,760
Mr. Yu is looking for me.

811
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:30,550
I'm meeting him at Lijun
to discuss business.

812
00:34:31,599 --> 00:34:32,720
I might be late,

813
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:33,440
don't wait up.

814
00:34:34,559 --> 00:34:35,479
Go to bed first.

815
00:34:47,039 --> 00:34:47,960
Feng Jianqi,

816
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,400
you're so timid.

817
00:34:50,410 --> 00:34:52,240
You don't even fight back
when people hit you.

818
00:34:53,039 --> 00:34:54,599
What did my sister even see in you?

819
00:34:56,639 --> 00:34:57,920
Are you even a man?

820
00:35:06,119 --> 00:35:06,960
Shen Minghui,

821
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,960
I've had enough of you.

822
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:10,599
You got the guts

823
00:35:11,119 --> 00:35:12,720
for a real man's duel?

824
00:35:14,519 --> 00:35:15,320
What are we doing?

825
00:35:15,720 --> 00:35:16,440
You name it.

826
00:35:18,599 --> 00:35:20,880
Arm wrestling. You dare?

827
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:27,559
Come on.

828
00:35:28,119 --> 00:35:29,240
Show me

829
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:30,760
what man-strength you've got.

830
00:35:31,039 --> 00:35:31,960
Don't go easy on me.

831
00:35:33,119 --> 00:35:33,920
Come on.

832
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,240
Did we start?

833
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,119
Put some muscle into it!

834
00:35:51,639 --> 00:35:52,479
Use your strength!

835
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:03,960
See now?

836
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:06,750
I've been going easy
on you this whole time.

837
00:36:24,720 --> 00:36:26,360
Huh, the floor's pretty sturdy now.

838
00:36:27,479 --> 00:36:28,840
Shen Minghui, what are you doing?

839
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:31,479
Be careful! It was just fixed!

840
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,320
Mind your own business!

841
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:34,999
You looking for a beating?

842
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,280
Only tough when you're with her.

843
00:36:39,479 --> 00:36:41,119
You and I are mortal enemies now!

844
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,999
Honey, you were amazing.

845
00:36:44,599 --> 00:36:45,960
It's time to put him in his place.

846
