928
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,559
- Yes.
- No.

929
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:23,639
Who's she?

930
00:41:26,559 --> 00:41:27,720
The car owner's mom.

931
00:41:30,140 --> 00:41:32,980
